briefTitle: Genetic Counseling in African American Women
officialTitle: Genetic Counseling for Breast Cancer Susceptibility in African American Women
eligibilityCriteria:
Inclusion Criteria:

* Female
* African American or Black
* 5% to 10% prior probability of having a BRCA1 or BRCA2 mutation

Exclusion Criteria:

* Men
* Individuals who are not African American or Black
